#Spell:  Raise undead [9180]
#
Usage:   COLLECT 31 [days]

Required aura:  none
Time to cast:   as given

Undead [31] are dead bodies animated with foul magic, summoned from
their graves.  They fight with the same combat effectiveness as
peasants:  attack-1, defense-1.

One undead may be summoned per day from a graveyard.  Graveyards
furnish up to 30 undead each month.

One or two undead may decompose at the end of each month.
